周期很长，如果我们拿了别人的钱。想法想很长时间保持一致，是几乎不可能的。而且在小米内部造车大量的人才技术都可以直接用。我非常非常清楚，我觉得造车难度很大，光靠我一个人肯定不行。」 雷军称，我需要小米集团的每个人都能毫无保留的支持，我希望大家都能全力以赴，起造车，我们才有胜算，所以最后我们决定，小米全资自己扛，只要能把车做好我们在所不惜。是李斌和何小鹏劝我造车！雷军透露造车细节：曾拒绝百亿美元估值报价，三年试驾了 170 多辆车，笔记超 20 万字 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-dafa82f81bab89a604ed12e374e6307d_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/662051387"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/5qMx/y4wpl6EAMaCTEwOTQwMDQxMiDY6em0BjAAOPACQCJyCTY2MjA1MTM4N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1721477418.382660", "card_id": "Q_645798797", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 163}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个合格的大人应该是什么样子的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "应当怎么做？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-dce7db0876b40aa66c1b2fb44a4c72b6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/645798797"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/5qMx/y4wpl6EAMaCTEwNTc4ODQ5MiDkgOyuBjAAON4BQCNyCTY0NTc5ODc5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1721477418.382980", "card_id": "Q_661941171", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果是康熙帝时期爆发鸦片战争，康熙的历史评价还有那么高吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如果是康熙帝时期爆发鸦片战争，康熙的历史评价还有那么高吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3eaa7382f868d6a3f7e4eea7f136871c_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6619